```css

  #pools
    help   .pools help -> gives detailed info on pools commands.
    list   .pools list -> gives the list of all CCX pools.
    info   .pools info -> gives the info about all CCX pools.
```
```css

  #wallet
    help       .wallet help -> gives detailed info on wallet commands.
    register   .wallet register -> registers a new wallet for the user. You need to specify a valid CCX address.
    update     .wallet update -> updates the current user wallet with new CCX address.
    show       .wallet show -> gives the current wallet details for the user.
    deposit    .wallet deposit -> give the user info about how to deposit to his/her wallet
    balance    .wallet balance -> shows the current user wallet balance
    paymentid  .wallet paymentid -> generates a paymentId
```
```css

  #users
    help     .users help -> gives detailed info on users commands.
    all      .users all -> counts all users on the server..
    online   .users online -> counts all online users on the server.
    offline  .users offline -> counts all offline users on the server.
    ban      .users ban -> bans a user from the server.
    kick     .users kick -> kicks a user from the server.
```
```css

  #general
    help   .help -> shows you this help content.
    tip    .tip -> tip a user that also has a registered wallet.
    say    .say -> makes the bot say something as if he said it.
    purge  .purge -> purges last N messages from the channel. 
